# Monetization rules

Read `docs/MONETIZATION_STRATEGY.md` before changing pricing, paywall, or gates.

## Plans (Android paywall)

- **Yearly** ₹499/year — `yearly_subscription` — primary, “Best value”
- **Monthly** ₹99/month — `monthly_subscription`
- **Lifetime** ₹1,499 — `lifetime_unlock` — decoy (≥3× yearly)
- **Student yearly** ₹249 — `yearly_subscription_student` (optional, flag in `monetization.ts`)

## SSOT

- Copy & fallback prices: `src/config/monetization.ts`
- Play product IDs: `src/config/billing.ts`
- Shared paywall UI: `src/components/premium/PremiumPaywallBody.tsx`

## Free forever

Day widget, Year widget, Share — never paywall.

## Ethics

- 48h cooldown after dismissing interstitial paywall
- Trial reminders days 10, 13, 14 (in-app + local notifications)
